<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>אגם הוצאה לאור</title>

  <style>
    
    .root-container {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 500px;
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-family: Segoe UI;
    }
    h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
      color: #EF4B49;
    }
    h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, p, div, main, header, footer, table, tbody, tr, td {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    a {
      color: #FFFFFF !important;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .app-header {
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }
    .app-header img {
      width: 100px;
    }
    .app-header .top {
      background-color: #EF4B49;
      height: 10px;
      
    }
    .app-header .bottom {
      background-color: #2E2926;
      height: 50px;
      text-align: center;
    }



    .app-main {
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .app-main h1 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .app-main .releases {
      direction: rtl;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .app-main .releases .release-preview {
      text-align: start;
      width: 50%;
      padding-inline-end: 20px;
    }
    .app-main .releases .release-preview .type {
      background-color: #EF4B49;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      width: fit-content;
      padding: 0 8px;
    }
    .app-main .releases .release-preview img {
      height: 160px;
      width: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);
    }
    .app-main .releases .release-preview .desc {
      height: 120px;
      max-width: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }



    .app-footer {
      direction: rtl;
      text-align: center;
      color: #FFFFFF;
    }
    .app-footer h3 {
      color: #FFFFFF;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }
    .app-footer .contact {
      background-color: #2E2926;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .app-footer .contact p {
      padding-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .app-footer .follow {
      background-color: #EF4B49;
    }
    .follow .follow-content {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .follow .follow-content td:first-child {
      /*width: 95%;*/
      width: 100%;
    }
    .follow .follow-content td:last-child {
      width: 5%;
      position: relative;
    }
    .app-footer .follow .media-list {
      width: 90%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-spacing: 15px
    }
    .app-footer .follow h3 {
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }
    .app-footer .follow td {
      width: 50%;
      text-align: start;
    }
    .app-footer .follow td:first-child {
      text-align: end;
    }
    .app-footer .follow td:nth-child(2) {
      text-align: start;
    }
    .app-footer .follow td:only-child {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .app-footer .follow td:only-child a table {
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .app-footer .follow .media-list .media-preview a {
      display: block;
      color: #FFFFFF;
    }
    .app-footer .follow .media-list .media-preview a table {
      border-spacing: 5px;
    }
    .app-footer .follow .media-list .media-preview a td {
      width: unset;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .app-footer .follow .media-list .media-preview img {
      height: 40px;
    }
    .app-footer .follow .media-list .media-preview p {
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .design-credit-container {
      width: 0;
    }
    .app-footer .follow .design-credit {
      display: inline-block;
      text-align: start;
      width: 115px;
    }
    .app-footer .credits {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #F4CF7E;
      color: #1E1E1E;
    }
    .app-footer .credits p {
      padding: 10px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 450px) {
      .app-footer .follow .media-list .media-preview a {
        height: 25px;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
      .app-footer .follow .media-list {
        border-spacing: 25px
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="root-container">
    <div class="app-header">
      <div class="top"></div>
      <div class="bottom">
        <img src="https://images.megaphon.co.il/643eac15afc5d349300c087f/04bdced0-f235-11ed-bd54-939946bca13e.png" alt="אגם הוצאה לאור">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="app-main">
      <h1>
        {{title}}
      </h1>
      <table class="releases"><tbody>
        {{#each mapedChildrenReleases}}
          {{#if (isEven @index)}}
            <tr>
          {{/if}}

              <td class="release-preview">
                <p class="type">{{this.type}}</p>
                <img src="{{this.mainImage.0.src}}" :alt="{{this.title}}"/>
                <p class="sub-type">{{this.subType}}</p>
                <h3 class="title">{{this.title}}</h3>
                <div class="flex column gap10">
                  <p>מאת: {{this.author}}</p>
                  <div class="desc">{{{this.desc}}}</div>
                </div>
              </td>
              
          {{#if (isOdd @index)}}
            </tr>
          {{else if @last}}
              <td class="release-preview"></td>
            </tr>
          {{/if}}
        {{/each}}
      </tbody></table>
    </div>

    <div class="app-footer">
      <div class="contact">
        <h3>יצירת קשר</h3>
        <p>מנהלת שיווק ההוצאה נטע שרף שוכמן</p>
        <p>052-4069-444</p>
        <p>info.agambooks.co.il</p>
      </div>
      <div class="follow">
        <h3>עוקבים ונשארים מעודכנים</h3>
        <table class="media-list"><tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="media-preview">
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/agambooks/" target="_blank"><table><tbody><tr>
                <td>
                  <img src="https://images.megaphon.co.il/643eac15afc5d349300c087f/f1571270-f234-11ed-bd54-939946bca13e.png" alt="facebook">
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>אגם הוצאה לאור</p>
                </td>
              </tr></tbody></table></a>
            </td>
            <td class="media-preview">
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/agambooks/" target="_blank"><table><tbody><tr>
                <td>
                  <img src="https://images.megaphon.co.il/643eac15afc5d349300c087f/f44531b0-f234-11ed-bd54-939946bca13e.png" alt="instegram">
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>@agambooks</p>
                </td>
              </tr></tbody></table></a>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="media-preview">
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqLjZATnh7TIU4YOOZ4nU7A" target="_blank"><table><tbody><tr>
                <td>
                  <img src="https://images.megaphon.co.il/643eac15afc5d349300c087f/fe443ee0-f234-11ed-bd54-939946bca13e.png" alt="youtube">
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>אגם הוצאה לאור</p>
                </td>
              </tr></tbody></table></a>
            </td>
            <td class="media-preview">
              <a href="https://www.agambooks.com" target="_blank"><table><tbody><tr>
                <td>
                  <img src="https://images.megaphon.co.il/643eac15afc5d349300c087f/fbd031a0-f234-11ed-bd54-939946bca13e.png" alt="web">
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>agambooks.com</p>
                </td>
              </tr></tbody></table></a>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="media-preview" colspan="2">
              <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@agambooks_" target="_blank"><table><tbody><tr>
                <td>
                  <img src="https://images.megaphon.co.il/643eac15afc5d349300c087f/f6384f20-f234-11ed-bd54-939946bca13e.png" alt="tiktok">
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>_@agambooks</p>
                </td>
              </tr></tbody></table></a>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
